[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=MCNF Notification Hub
Comment=Slide-out mesh + desktop alert center (NOTIFY-3); Workstation-rank gated — Servers/Lighthouses are headless. OPT-IN (off by default): the applet bell already spawns the Hub on demand, so auto-opening the panel at login is opt-in. Set X-GNOME-Autostart-enabled=true (or enable in Settings ▸ Startup Applications) to have it open at login.
Exec=sh -c "mackesd role-gate --min-rank 2 && exec mde-notify-center"
Icon=magic-mesh
Terminal=false
NoDisplay=true
X-GNOME-Autostart-enabled=false
